==English==
===Noun===
'''hydrofoil'''
#{{nautical}} a [[wing]] attached to the [[hull]] of a [[ship]] that [[raise]]s it out of the [[water]] when travelling at speed and thus reduces [[drag]]
#{{nautical}} a [[vessel]] equipped with such a device
